It becomes even, the effort with which Barack Obama, president to the reputation of wise, reproduced the strategy of his predecessor on the Afghan issue, that he considered himself as simple..
When he eventually leave its doctrine so, it turned out that he had in carbon paper since the Iraqi scenario of Bush three years ago.
