It will take a long time before another offer is being made in Iraq..
concerns about security, corroborated by massive coordinated bombings, Tuesday, and political instability, while the U.S. military troops withdraw have slowed the American oil companies, preventing them from entering with more force in Iraq, which has the third largest crude oil reserve in the world, say analysts...
