New tools for the expertise of cars
In these days of bad weather and accidents, the car garages are not the only winners.
Every day, thousands of cars that have suffered a disaster are reduced to a garage, where an expert to assess the damage and the cost of the repair.
disaster is different, and the calculation of the cost of parts and labor time can be a long and complex.
calculate the cost of a compensation of between 20 000 and 30 000 euros, including parts and labor can take two or three hours.
, with the assistance of the latest computer tools, it would be a matter of minutes.
It is for this reason that almost 100% of experts use of such systems.
of services and solutions for the assessment of claims and maintenance are dedicated to the collection of information provided by the manufacturers, and then treat them and offer their customers in the form of a useful tool.
In Spain, Audatex, the North American group, is the company leader; 80% of the estimates are made with its products.
companies competing in the field of evaluation tools and the development of information on the sector are GtMotive and Eurotax.
The work with the data provided by manufacturers is far from simple..
